name: George Bayford
description: I would enjoy a romantic, sincere, honest and fun-loving partner who likes to be kept busy. It would be great if she would enjoy the outdoors, travel and casual dinning. I would like a one-to-one relationship based on trust – friendship/lover. I feel good communication and respect for each other is important. I want a partner who wants to make a lifetime commitment to making each other happy. I believe that natural chemistry between two people is a must and is the first step in establishing a good and meaningful relationship. I enjoy meeting open minded people who enjoy exploring new places and trying new things. Anyone who is easy-going, sociable, and loves to laugh will get along great with me.
